overview: Adam and Eve had ideal conditions for getting to know each other, they were naked and without any competition. Today, however, finding a partner can become a pretty tough task. The relaxing comedy Sezn@mka, whose creators were inspired by real experiences and stories, will show all sorts of vicissitudes, believable and unbelievable situations and encounters during the thorny journey to find the right counterpart.
title: Sezn@mka
